    AuditEvent
    A simple Bean to encapsulate an auditable event.
    AuditInterceptor

    BaseFinder
    Try to use the generic methods here for the simple cases.

    Provides a wrapper for each method of Hibernate Session.

    Hibernate Interceptor implementation.

    This class is used by scripts to launch the session factory and bootstrap the database.

    BusinessContextStatsFacade

    DatabaseHelperFactoryBean

    DatabasePostInitializer
    This class entails post-initialisation process.
    DatabaseType  
    DatabaseVersion

    DefaultSessionFactory

    HiberCache

    IndexManager

    InterceptionDepthLimiter

  • Exception Summary
